        "localization": {
          "name": "Phase Out",
          "description": "Exchanges 1 random enemy with an Imposter. The exchanged enemy will be sent to the front of the enemy reinforcements. This exchange will fail if the target is Immovable or if there are less than 4 enemies on the battlefield (no imposter will be added).\n\nThen pulls the user away from the battlefield to the front of your reinforcements. If there are no ally reinforcements, adds enough Elmina's (max 3) to the ally team to still pull the user away to reinforcements.\n\nUsable if the user has defeated 1+ units with attacks while on the battlefield, and there are 2 non-conjured allies on the battlefield.",
          "selected": "User steps back, may exchange enemy with imposter"
        }
